{"snp1.5:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 1.5 ","snp1.5:0.2":"Cundasutta ","snp1.5:1.1":"“Pucchami munim pahutapannam, ","snp1.5:1.2":"(iti cundo kammaraputto) ","snp1.5:1.3":"Buddham dhammassamim vitatanham; ","snp1.5:1.4":"Dvipaduttamam sarathinam pavaram, ","snp1.5:1.5":"Kati loke samana tadingha bruhi”. ","snp1.5:2.1":"“Caturo samana na pancamatthi, ","snp1.5:2.2":"(cundati bhagava) ","snp1.5:2.3":"Te te avikaromi sakkhiputtho; ","snp1.5:2.4":"Maggajino maggadesako ca, ","snp1.5:2.5":"Magge jivati yo ca maggadusi”. ","snp1.5:3.1":"“Kam maggajinam vadanti buddha, ","snp1.5:3.2":"(iti cundo kammaraputto) ","snp1.5:3.3":"Maggakkhayi katham atulyo hoti; ","snp1.5:3.4":"Magge jivati me bruhi puttho, ","snp1.5:3.5":"Atha me avikarohi maggadusim”. ","snp1.5:4.1":"“Yo tinnakathankatho visallo, ","snp1.5:4.2":"Nibbanabhirato ananugiddho; ","snp1.5:4.3":"Lokassa sadevakassa neta, ","snp1.5:4.4":"Tadim maggajinam vadanti buddha. ","snp1.5:5.1":"Paramam paramanti yodha natva, ","snp1.5:5.2":"Akkhati vibhajate idheva dhammam; ","snp1.5:5.3":"Tam kankhachidam munim anejam, ","snp1.5:5.4":"Dutiyam bhikkhunamahu maggadesim. ","snp1.5:6.1":"Yo dhammapade sudesite, ","snp1.5:6.2":"Magge jivati sannato satima; ","snp1.5:6.3":"Anavajjapadani sevamano, ","snp1.5:6.4":"Tatiyam bhikkhunamahu maggajivim. ","snp1.5:7.1":"Chadanam katvana subbatanam, ","snp1.5:7.2":"Pakkhandi kuladusako pagabbho; ","snp1.5:7.3":"Mayavi asannato palapo, ","snp1.5:7.4":"Patirupena caram sa maggadusi. ","snp1.5:8.1":"Ete ca pativijjhi yo gahattho, ","snp1.5:8.2":"Sutava ariyasavako sapanno; ","snp1.5:8.3":"Sabbe netadisati natva, ","snp1.5:8.4":"Iti disva na hapeti tassa saddha; ","snp1.5:8.5":"Katham hi dutthena asampaduttham, ","snp1.5:8.6":"Suddham asuddhena samam kareyya”ti. ","snp1.5:8.7":"Cundasuttam pancamam. "}